#!/usr/bin/env ssc
---
name: bench-fib
description: Recursive Fibonacci — exercises function-call overhead.
---

# Fibonacci

```scalascript
def fib(n: Int): Int = if n < 2 then n else fib(n - 1) + fib(n - 2)

val n      = 28
val t0     = nanoTime()
val result = fib(n)
val t1     = nanoTime()

println(s"BENCH_MS: ${(t1 - t0) / 1000000}")
println(s"result=$result")
```
